    <published>2023-07-26T13:04:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-07-26T13:12:23.678Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一次帶 Samyang 35mm F2.8 定焦鏡出去街拍，體驗還是很不錯的，個人來說很喜歡，相比 F4 顯著不少的虛化感很棒。唯一就是會有相對比較明顯的 color fringing ，需要後期處理。</p><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00808.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00808.JPG"></p><span id="more"></span><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00810.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00810.JPG"></p><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00817.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00817.JPG"></p><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00829.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00829.JPG"></p><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00840.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00840.JPG"></p><p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00842.JPG&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00842.JPG"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;第一次帶 Samyang 35mm F2.8 定焦鏡出去街拍，體驗還是很不錯的，個人來說很喜歡，相比 F4 顯著不少的虛化感很棒。唯一就是會有相對比較明顯的 color fringing ，需要後期處理。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00808.JPG&amp;default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/Photography-20230726/0726-ILCE-7C-AYA00808.JPG&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
